    {
      "content": "<img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" class=\"\" style=\"width: 475px; height: 105px;\"><p><br></p>This demo profile walks you through every feature of the app — click, edit, move cards around: everything here is meant to be explored!<div><br>&nbsp;\n<div>\n</div><div>🗑️ You can delete it anytime from the sidebar, exactly like any other profile.</div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780844692578,
      "w": 547,
      "h": 323,
      "color": "blue"
    },
    {
      "content": "✏️ <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Create &amp; format a card</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div></div><div><ul><li>Click \"+ New card\" to create one\n</li><li>Format it with the toolbar: bold, lists, links, colors, images…\n</li><li>Click a card to edit it, or use its ✏️ button</li></ul></div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780844861033,
      "w": 347,
      "h": 326,
      "color": "yellow"
    },
    {
      "content": "📌 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Pin, color, organize</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div>\n</div><div><ul><li>Pin important cards to keep them at the top\n</li><li>Give them a color to spot them at a glance\n</li><li>Turn on Edit mode (🖊️) to freely resize and reposition cards — like the different sizes you see in this very profile!</li></ul></div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780844901336,
      "w": 679,
      "h": 329,
      "color": "pink"
    },
    {
      "content": "🔍 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Search</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div>\n</div><div><ul><li>Type a word in the search bar to filter cards in the current profile\n</li><li>Add / before your search to look across all your profiles at once</li></ul></div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780845104210,
      "h": 264,
      "color": "green"
    },
    {
      "content": "📁 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Multiple profiles</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div>\n</div><div><ul><li>Create as many profiles as you like (Work, Personal, Projects…) with the + button\n</li><li>Click a profile in the sidebar to switch to it\n</li><li>Reorder them by drag-and-drop</li></ul></div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780845023727,
      "w": 523,
      "h": 266,
      "color": "purple"
    },
    {
      "content": "📤 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Export, import, back up</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div></div><div><ul><li>Export saves the current profile as JSON, Export all saves every profile\n</li><li>Import loads one or more JSON files back in\n</li></ul><div><br></div>💡 Tip: in Settings ⚙️ → Export, choose a folder so your exports are saved there automatically</div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780845211923,
      "w": 547,
      "h": 266
    },
    {
      "content": "📡 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Share between devices</span><div><b><br></b><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"></span><div></div><div><ul><li>The Share button generates a 6-character code. Enter it on another device to transfer a whole profile peer-to-peer — no server, no account needed.</li></ul></div></div>",
      "isPinned": false,
      "createdAt": 1780845294551,
      "w": 532,
      "h": 169,
      "color": "orange"
    },
    {
      "content": "🚀 <span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Your turn!\n</span><div>\n</div><div><br></div><div>Everything is stored locally on your device — your data belongs to you.\n</div><div>When you're ready, delete this demo profile via the ❌ icon next to its name in the sidebar, and start your own! 😊</div><div>\n</div><div>\n</div>",
